titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on 4-Y3-(4-chlorophenyl)-3-(3,4-dimethoxyphenyl)-1-oxo-2-propen yl?morpholine.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

bill.summary:
2/13/2008--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on 4-Y3-(4-chlorophenyl)-3-(3,4-dimethoxyphenyl)-1-oxo-2-propen yl?morpholine.
